•	Discuss whether the tournament has become more/less
    	predictable over time
•	Since the start of our data analysis range of 2008, the upset rate has increased or decreased from 20% in 2008 but has not gone above 35% or below 15%. Recently, the upset rate has sharply decreased from 2024, going from 30% to ~17%.
•	Since 2008, the upset rate has varied between 17% and 35%, roughly. There is a slight upward trend from 2008 to 2024 of 0.04% per year. However, it is not statistically significant because the p-value is 0.883
